<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-width: 100%;
            width: 100% !important;
            height: 100% !important;
        }
        .email-container {
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .email-header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .email-body {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }
        .email-footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>Welcome to Chatteree</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Dear User,</p>
            <p>We're excited to have you on board. To verify your email address, please use the following 6-digit code:</p>
            <h2 style="text-align: center;"><%= otp %></h2>
            <p>If you did not request this code, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>Best regards,</p>
            <p>The Chatteree Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>